Python Task 3: Data Logging and Visualisation [10 marks]
In this task, you will write a Python script that records user data to a CSV file, performs simple analysis with pandas and NumPy, and visualises the results using matplotlib.

Task 3a: CSV File Setup
1.      Create a new file named people.csv with the columns:  Name, Age [1 mark]

